<!-- Banner -->
<div class="banner-peetayers" style="background-image: linear-gradient(-225deg, rgba(0,101,168,0.6) 0%, rgba(0,36,61,0.6) 50%), url('<%=image_path "https://source.unsplash.com/collection/865018/1000x300"%>');">
  <div class="banner-peetayers-content">
    <h1>Welcome</h1>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- End Banner -->

<div class="container">
  <div class="body">
    <div class="row">

      <div class="column-1">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-3">
          <div class="polaroid flo">
            <div class="polaroid-img" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.2)), url('<%=image_path "peetayers/nicolas.jpg" %>');">
            </div>
            <p class="polaroid-text"><strong>Paquit & Nico, 30/27 ans<strong></p>
            <p class="polaroid-desc">"I know Lille inside out!"</p>
          </div>
          <br>

          <div class="infos">
            <div class="infos-title text-center">
              <p><strong>Information checked</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="infos-content">
              <ul><p><i class="far fa-check-circle"></i> Official ID</p></ul>
              <ul><p><i class="far fa-check-circle"></i> Phone</p></ul>
              <ul><p><i class="far fa-check-circle"></i> Email</p></ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="column-2">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-9">

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space1 text-center">
                <div class="space1-title">
                  <h3>Hello, We're Paquit & Nico!</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="space1-content">
                  <p>Lille, France ° since always</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Available services</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <div class="row">
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/suitcase.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Prepare your trip</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/location.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Housing services</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/medical-history.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Help with admins</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/chat.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Speak local</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/cheers.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Local tips</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/masks.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Cultural outings</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/football.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Play sports</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/welcome.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Be welcomed</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Languages?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>French & English</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Why do you like Lille?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>Une ville à taille humaine, ou tout peut se faire rapidement à pied, vélo , transport en commun (métro, bus, tram), bien situé entre Londres Paris Bruxelles, les gens sont vraiment accueillants et on peut également trouver de la bonne biére et il est aussi possible de faire beaucoup de sport différents.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Your favorite spots in Lille?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>Le boudin bar, la citadelle, canal de la deule.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Why do you want to become a Peetayer?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>Pour aider les étrangers à trouver rapidement leurs repères et limiter le temps perdu dans le superflu.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>What are your interests?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>Sport, cinéma</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>What about Paquit & Nico?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>Jeune homme sportif étudiant en médecine, aimant la ville de Lille et le Nord et ses bières.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Which countries have you visited?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>dans le cadre des vacances : sri lanka, madagascar, thaïlande, birmanie, islande</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

